    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Adventurer's Armory pg. 19</em><br /><strong>Price</strong> 5 cp/mug; <strong>Weight</strong> 1/2 lb.<br /><strong>Category</strong> Food/Drink</p><h2 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px\" title=\"PFS Legal\" />Description</h2><p>This ale is the standard beer drunk in Absalom. The recipe was said to be the last beer Cayden Cailean had before he undertook the <em>Test of the Starstone</em>. The hops for this beer were originally grown on the Isle of Kortos, but the massive brewery now imports from Andoran and Taldor.</p>",
